{"tid":2203245,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：檢測計劃盛惠香港民族5.3億 當中3.7億為親共醫護及檢測中心人員酬金","createTime":"2020-09-15T08:06:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T08:21:47.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1dba8b429891b5c0bd49ce3a68dd6710d35e5b08","tid":2203245,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:06:34.000Z","msg":"政府斥資5.3億推行普及社區檢測計劃 臨時實驗室運作費用由中央負責<br />\n<br />\n為期14日的普及社區檢測計劃昨日結束，公務員事務局長聶德權表示，特區政府斥資5.3億元，當中七成，即3.7億元是醫護人員及檢測中心支援人員酬金，其餘開支包括檢測中心保安、物流運輸、租用場地及防護裝備等費用。至於位於中山紀念公園體育館的臨時實驗室，運作及化驗人員的服務費用由中央政府負責。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權指，計劃至今有178.3萬人採樣，過程順利，重申達到政策目的。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2357288\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2357288&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuRF66oQwccw1TbdUPfwT%2FAY%3D&h=c633f177\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2357288</a>"},{"pid":"356d5a9a597cab173edb36e28c94e81749135ed0","tid":2203245,"uid":53672,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/duY4ADU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FduY4ADU.jpg&h=b1b5e049&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"594d094e26ade6694c7d52b592eafdb5c103c3aa","tid":2203245,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:12:25.000Z","msg":"浪費納稅人金錢"},{"pid":"b0379f820223d898cdd5b2e85adf61b8e9764360","tid":2203245,"uid":12208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:13:55.000Z","msg":"党fatfat<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b31aa37e2b07b41e32bd07dc6f85d955a087a5","tid":2203245,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T08:14:02.000Z","msg":"為咗林鄭面子，浪費5億幾"},{"pid":"51c7ce45bdf5e53da29296b1b79354e36c537a19","tid":2203245,"uid":188482,"